V0110_01_00_00_0.text: The outcome of a Duel is determined 99% of the time by one's intelligence.

V0110_01_00_00_1.text: I shall prove that to you!

V0110_01_00_01_0.text: Let's see if your tactics can rival mine!

V0110_01_00_02_0.text: You claim to be the #1 Duelist in Duel Academy.

V0110_01_00_02_1.text: But I designed a whole new Deck specifically to take down your Elemental HEROES!

V0110_01_00_03_0.text: You're just a problem to be solved. A theorem to be cracked.

V0110_01_00_03_1.text: Which I shall do with this Deck, Chazz!

V0110_01_00_10_0.text:
Uh, hello!
I was here the whole time!

V0110_01_00_10_1.text: I was here even before you showed up!

V0110_03_00_01_0.text: It's about time to end this!

V0110_03_00_02_0.text: There is nothing I need to fear.

V0110_03_00_04_0.text:
Argh...
I can't figure out your algorithm!

V0110_05_00_00_0.text: With my optimal Deck and flawless draw, I have perfected the theory of Dueling!

V0110_06_01_02_0.text: Only the unprepared would fall for such a move.

V0110_07_09_00_0.text: I flip over my face-down card!

V0110_08_00_00_0.text: I activate the Spell Card, Bonding - H2O

V0110_08_00_00_1.text: With 2 Hydrogeddon and 1 Oxygeddon on my field...

V0110_08_00_00_2.text: It's simple science to create water!

V0110_08_00_01_0.text: Ah, just the moment I was waiting for.

V0110_08_00_01_1.text:
I activate my Trap!
Cursed Seal of the Forbidden Spell!

V0110_08_00_02_0.text: I activate the Quick-Play Spell, Reload!

V0110_08_00_03_0.text:
I activate my Spell Card!
Double Spell!

V0110_08_00_04_0.text:
I activate my Spell Card!
A Wingbeat of Giant Dragon!

V0110_08_00_05_0.text:
I activate my Continuous Trap!
Spirit Barrier!

V0110_08_00_06_0.text:
I activate my Spell Card!
Nobleman of Extermination!

V0110_08_00_07_0.text:
My Trap Card activates!
Ring of Destruction!

V0110_08_00_08_0.text:
My Trap Card activates!
Magic Cylinder!

V0110_08_00_09_0.text:
I activate my Spell Card!
Card Destruction!

V0110_08_00_10_0.text:
I activate my Spell Card!
Graceful Charity!

V0110_08_00_11_0.text:
I activate my Spell Card!
Foolish Burial!

V0110_08_00_13_0.text: The Trap Card, Mischief of the Yokai!

V0110_08_00_16_0.text: I activate the Ritual Spell, Litmus Doom Ritual!

V0110_09_00_01_0.text:
Do you know what happens when oxygen mixes with fire?
You shall find out now!

V0110_09_00_03_1.text: When it destroys your monster in battle, I can Special Summon another Hydrogeddon from my Deck!

V0110_09_00_10_0.text: Goka, the Pyre of Malice's effect activates!

V0110_09_00_15_0.text: White Magician Pikeru, activate your effect!

V0110_09_00_15_1.text:
Sigh...
You're more than just my card crush!

V0110_09_00_16_0.text: Litmus Doom Swordsman, unleash your effect!

V0110_11_00_00_0.text: I Summon a monster in Attack Position!

V0110_11_01_00_0.text: I Summon a monster in Defense Position!

V0110_13_00_00_0.text: The waters often appear serene, but sudden riptides swallow the earth whole!

V0110_13_00_07_0.text: I've invited the emissary of darkness! Red Ogre!

V0110_13_00_10_0.text: A single spark can turn into a roaring inferno!

V0110_13_00_10_1.text: Burn! Goka, the Pyre of Malice!

V0110_13_00_11_0.text: I Special Summon a Level 8 monster!

V0110_13_00_12_0.text: Don't judge a monster by its cover.

V0110_13_00_15_0.text: I don't recall putting this card in my Deck. How did it get in here?

V0110_13_00_15_1.text:
I'll worry about that later.
Come on out, White Magician Pikeru!

V0110_13_00_16_0.text: This card isn't affected by Traps nor can it be destroyed in battle. He is truly immortal!

V0110_19_00_07_0.text:
Hmm, is this the right moment to attack... 
Yes, I believe it is!
Go, Red Ogre!

V0110_19_00_15_0.text:
Sigh... White Magician Pikeru, you truly are the queen of my Deck...
Ack! I have to shake off my card crush and focus!

V0110_19_00_16_0.text: Litmus Doom Swordsman, give 'em a taste of your steel!

V0110_21_00_00_0.text: There are no errors in my equations.

V0110_21_00_01_0.text: My opening moves have put me in an ideal situation.

V0110_28_00_00_1.text: I simply executed my formulas to perfection.

V0110_28_00_01_0.text: Dueling is nothing more than a numbers game. And the numbers never lie.

V0110_28_00_02_0.text:
Phew...
My experimental Deck came through.

V0110_28_00_03_0.text: As you always say, that was a sweet game.

V0110_28_00_03_1.text: Now I'm the #1 Duelist at the Academy.

V0110_29_00_00_1.text:
My formulas were perfect!
What could have gone wrong?

V0110_29_00_01_0.text: One errant mistake threw my deck’s delicate balance completely off.

V0110_29_00_02_1.text: A single error in my play led to disastrous consequences.

V0110_29_00_03_0.text: Countless equations, many theorems... But I have yet to solve the formula known as you, Jaden.

V0110_29_00_03_1.text: You may have beaten this Deck, but you can be assured that there will be another.

V0110_30_00_00_0.text: I'll use this time to calculate new Dueling equations.

V0110_30_00_02_0.text:
Don't try to take me off my game with your card crushes!
They're irrational, illogical, ridiculous!

V0110_33_00_00_0.text: This is the formula for victory!

V0110_33_00_02_0.text: Your Deck's a problem that I've already solved!

V0110_34_00_05_0.text: According to my calculations, you have less than a 1% chance to win.

V0110_34_00_06_0.text: Like the butterfly that sheds its cocoon, I must shed my past!

V0110_34_00_07_0.text: Keep your cool, Bastion. Don't get distracted by those silly card crushes. You’ve always been above that!

V0110_35_00_01_0.text:
It's finally my turn. 
Took long enough.

V0110_26_00_02_0.text: Ah, so that's what you were planning.

V0110_27_00_01_0.text: This was a necessary expense to execute my plan!

V0110_27_00_02_0.text: I must clear my mind to escape this predicament!
